% rebase('layout.tpl', title='Company History', year=year)

<div class="container py-4">
    <!-- Main header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h1 style="font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #222;">The OrtPillow Journey</h1>
        <p class="lead" style="font-size: 1.3rem; color: #555;">From a garage startup to Russia's orthopedic sleep leader</p>
        <hr style="width: 100px; margin: 1.5rem auto; opacity: 0.2;">
    </div>

    <!-- Main content -->
    <div class="row">
        <!-- Text block -->
        <div class="col-lg-8" style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.7;">
            <div class="section-block mb-5">
                <h3 class="section-title" style="font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 600; color: #333; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">The Vision (2016-2017)</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">During their final year at Saint Petersburg State University, Kirill Baranov (Engineering), Roman Gavrilov (Business), and Mahach Gadzhiev (Medicine) discovered a shared frustration - poor quality orthopedic pillows failing to address basic sleep needs. Their late-night discussions in campus labs revealed:</p>
                
                <ul class="mb-4" style="padding-left: 1.5rem;">
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;"><strong style="color: #0056b3;">82%</strong> of test subjects reported neck pain with standard pillows</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;">Hospital pillows lacked proper cervical support</li>
                    <li>No Russian-made products combined medical expertise with modern materials</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="my-5">
                    <h4 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #333;">First Workshop</h4>
                    <img src="/static/images/garage_start.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm w-100" alt="First workshop" style="max-height: 300px; object-fit: cover;">
                    <p class="mt-2 text-center" style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666;"><em>The original OrtPillow workshop (2017)</em></p>
                </div>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">After graduating, they converted Kirill's family garage into Russia's first dedicated orthopedic pillow workshop. Using Mahach's medical diagrams and Roman's crowdfunding campaign, they produced 12 functional prototypes.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="section-block mb-5">
                <h3 class="section-title" style="font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 600; color: #333; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">Breakthrough Years (2018-2020)</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">The team faced three critical challenges:</p>
                <ol class="mb-4" style="padding-left: 1.5rem;">
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;"><strong style="color: #0056b3;">Material Science:</strong> Tested 38 foam composites before perfecting their proprietary blend</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;"><strong style="color: #0056b3;">Medical Approval:</strong> Conducted clinical trials at City Hospital №1</li>
                    <li><strong style="color: #0056b3;">Production:</strong> Developed custom sewing patterns for optimal support</li>
                </ol>

                <div class="my-5">
                    <h4 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #333;">First Major Success</h4>
                    <img src="/static/images/first_team.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm w-100" alt="OrtPillow team" style="max-height: 300px; object-fit: cover;">
                    <p class="mt-2 text-center" style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #666;"><em>Core team celebrating first hospital order (2019)</em></p>
                </div>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Their persistence paid off when renowned neurologist Dr. Elena Volkova published a study showing <strong style="color: #0056b3;">67% improvement</strong> in sleep quality using OrtPillow products. This led to their first major contract - supplying 500 pillows to Saint Petersburg Children's Hospital.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="section-block mb-5">
                <h3 class="section-title" style="font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 600; color: #333; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">Innovation Era (2021-Present)</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">With their <strong style="color: #0056b3;">3 patented technologies</strong>, OrtPillow now leads in:</p>
                <ul class="mb-4" style="padding-left: 1.5rem;">
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;"><strong style="color: #0056b3;">Temperature Regulation:</strong> Gel-infused foam prevents overheating</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;"><strong style="color: #0056b3;">Custom Fit:</strong> 7 firmness levels for personalized support</li>
                    <li><strong style="color: #0056b3;">Hygiene:</strong> Antimicrobial fabric approved for medical use</li>
                </ul>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Today, our <strong style="color: #0056b3;">1,500m² facility</strong> produces over <strong style="color: #0056b3;">15,000 pillows monthly</strong>, supplied to:</p>
                <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem;">
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">27 rehabilitation centers across Russia</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">12 professional sports teams</li>
                    <li>8 European medical distributors</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Photos block -->
